      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SHIMMERING LIGHT (2) missed the frame latest when sixth at this track (19.44) but scored four back at Q Lakeside (21.78). Form is hard to fault from this box, with a win and four minor placings from five starts. Can make amends. SORSOGON SMILE (1) turned in a solid run last start over 352m at Q Lakeside finishing 5th and beaten only 4.5 lengths (20.15). Warrants plenty of respect. VERACIOUS VAL (6) was quick to begin and led throughout to record a strong 1.5 lengths win (30.23) at Q Parklands in Mix 5. Has failed to finish in the placings from two starts here. Expected to measure up again. SHE'S A KIWI (7) placed last start and is in the mix again.",
